sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant DB

    User->>Frontend: Enter keyword + filters
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/products?keyword&category&price
    Backend->>DB: Query products (name regex, optional filters)
    DB-->>Backend: Matching products
    Backend-->>Frontend: Products JSON (paginated)
    Frontend-->>User: Show results and pages
